Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.09,0:01:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura, you've got it all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not peeking!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.90,0:01:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And here I told you not to...\N{\i1}not to...not to...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.93,0:01:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me...Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.83,0:01:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it morning already...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.67,0:01:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't...feel like I slept at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he get up already...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.32,0:02:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His stuff... {\i1}Sai's stuff is gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where...did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Captain Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That jerk, that jerk Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.19,0:02:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai's outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your timing's perfect. I've got something\NI want to ask you to do for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:05.93,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(766,585)}Untitled\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So you draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're foul-mouthed,\Nbut you've also got a sensitive side, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That fake smile...\NSo you're still not through hitting me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not quite...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kidding!\NI just came to check out your picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering what you were drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, I thought you were drawing\Na landscape
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,since you're drawing out here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's an abstract, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the title of this drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't decided on one yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.05,0:05:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The name of this drawing, a title.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got something in mind, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't laugh, so tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've drawn tens of thousands\Nof pictures...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've never given one a title.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So this doesn't have one, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're supposed to give\Na title to a picture, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a portrait,\Nyou give it the name of the person...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Or with other pictures,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you use the situation,\Nyour feelings or emotions at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,To be exact, I couldn't title\None of my drawings even if I wanted to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing comes to mind.\NI don't...feel anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder you can only say\Nsuch callous things!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time for us to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Yamato told me\Nto come get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This drawing's nothing special!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...\NJust like your dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be straight with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've got a problem, stop the fake smiles\Nand tell me straight to my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you on anytime\Nyou want to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... You want to fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,no problem with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll catch up once I've tidied up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This...isn't printed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you draw this, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:07:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's a picture book, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,can I take a look\Nat it along the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not finished yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't hand this over to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my older brother's book, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he said he drew it himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you... Please come again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So has your rapport improved?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to be with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So would you have preferred\Ncontrol by fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's okay. Our rapport has improved!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto looks like he's enjoying himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fake smile\Nany way you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You yourself said that\Na smile is the best way
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to get through a tough situation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't feel anything.\N{\i1}I don't care about you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Captain Yamato?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we going to the trouble\Nof coming through here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Yamato!\NWhat's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the path we were on\Nwas the right way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Lady Tsunade has told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The information Sakura\Ngot might be a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a possibility that\Nthe Akatsuki might be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting to ambush us\Nat the Tenchi Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They might be after you, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think there's a great possibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but you can never be too careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll proceed along a covert route\Nas much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,until we reach the Tenchi Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.99,0:12:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this spot is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.11,0:12:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll rest here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're going to camp out,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,we should use the cave we just passed by\Ninstead of this wide open area...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Step back, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wood Style: Four Pillar House Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll camp out here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you can call something\Nlike this camping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, so this is what it looks\Nlike on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite spacious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I think our room just might\Nhold some promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:44.09,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(423,147)}Welcome\NTeam Kakashi
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's surprisingly bare, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, it's better than sleeping outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Break time, break time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.18,0:14:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if only we had a bath, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.15,0:14:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather around, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to ask\Nyou something, Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about the Akatsuki's Sasori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasori...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask you sooner,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but I promised that we weren't going to\Ntalk about stuff like that yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to tell me everything today...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who's ever\Nseen Sasori in person, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,For the time being,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've received a file on Sasori\Nfrom the Hidden Sand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But tell me in as much detail\Nas you can
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,about his personality, behavior,\Nmannerisms and habits if he has any.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The spy who's infiltrated\NOrochimaru's organization thinks
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasori is going to meet him\Nat the Tenchi Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They might see us through immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's probably best to approach\Nby transforming into Sasori.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If Sasori doesn't show up\Nat the Tenchi Bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,then the spy might not, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a distinct possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there'd be no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:16:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a spy is a very risky act, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means the spy is probably\Nbeing quite cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then are you going to transform\Ninto Sasori, Captain Yamato?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll probably have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems he always remained\Nhidden inside this Hiruko puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm probably the right one for this\Nsince I can use the Wood Style Ninjutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, assuming this turns out\Nto be an Akatsuki trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll approach him alone at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At midday in ten days,\N{\i1}go to the Tenchi Bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}located in the Village Hidden\N{\i1}in the Grass!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got a spy working as one\N{\i1}of Orochimaru's subordinates...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was supposed to rendezvous...\N{\i1}with him...there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The way he talked being near death...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he was lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was indeed a spy\Ncalled Yura in the Sand Village...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.47,0:17:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just assuming\Nsomething goes wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys stand by until\NI give you instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, there's no doubting...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that spy is probably\Nconsiderably powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.67,0:18:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now for the main issue...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me explain the mission in\Na little more detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.01,0:18:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Our goal is just to arrest the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We must not let him die,\Neven if we end up having to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll lose an important source of\Ninformation if the target is killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And a mission like this is more difficult\Nthan just killing an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,As this is a delicate mission,\NI will make the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And you guys will be my back-up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The strategy is simple.\NFirst, I restrain the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Second, if I should fail\Nto restrain the target
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and this turns into a battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you guys shift to battle formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I will give you a signal when\NI want you to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the event of the second case,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you are to operate with\Nthe Buddy System.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Buddy System?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When one person takes action,\Na partner always backs you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Reciprocal back-up is\Na fundamental rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You know about this, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! That, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it together, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm going to determine\Nthe Buddy Teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,First, Sakura and I will be one team!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.33,0:19:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the other team will be...\NNaruto and Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:19:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with him...?
